name: Mogetius

attributes.attribute: identified by the Romans with their deity of war, Mars

sources: Monaghan, Patricia. The Encyclopedia of Celtic Mythology and Folklore. Checkmark Books, 2008.
text: A deity by the name of Mogetius is known to the Continental Celts from a couple of inscriptions. Inscriptions indicate that this god was not very popular. The Romans, however, equated Mogetius with their own god of war, Mars.
